<p>For instance, on Youtube, if you are watching a video and wants to search other stuff, the currently playing video will be interrupted. It can't happen with music. Users must be able to interact with the system without messing up what what is currently playing. Despite it may represent big changes on the software architecture it is a fundamental characteristic.</p>

